    "usecase_voting": "@Lineup Make voting cards for a board budget vote on June 18 at 5pm in Town Hall Room 2B, accent green, RSVP/ballot link https://vote.example.org/budget-2026 — voters Nadia (Seat 1), Omar (Seat 2), Priya (Seat 3), Stefan (Seat 4), and Clara as Chair.",
